# claude — session scratch is ignored, but persistent memory IS committed
# so cross-session/cross-machine sessions can read it (CLAUDE.md says
# "Read this file at the start of every session").
# Use .claude/* (not .claude/) so the negation below can re-include.
.claude/*
!.claude/memory.md

